						               													<description>Are you a fan of Imposter or Murder Mystery games? Then Imposters On Mars is the perfect game for you. It turns your house (location) into a real-life game board &amp;mdash; a colony on Mars. Beware, an Imposter is sabotaging your hard work. Complete jobs and work together to repair the colony. Keep a close eye and figure out who the Imposters are. Vote and cast them out. But be careful not to vote for the wrong person.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Beware, an Imposter is sabotaging your hard work. Complete jobs and work together to repair the colony. Keep a close eye and figure out who the Imposters are. Vote and cast them out. But be careful not to vote for the wrong person.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your house is now a real-life game board. The rooms in your house (or location) are the game board's spaces where you&amp;rsquo;ll complete mini-games. These mini-games are called Jobs. Every Player starts with four cards. The first choose a Player&amp;rsquo;s color. The Player then takes their matching color Vote card. The third card determines who the Imposters are. Finally, every Player chooses a Career and their Job order.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every room is set up with a mini-game (matching, math, memory, etc.). These mini-games are called Jobs. Players complete Jobs and share proof of completing them. Playing as the Imposter gives you the ability to sabotage Jobs. Imposters are randomly selected. Imposters sabotage Jobs and force Players to freeze their gameplay for a period of time. This allows the Imposter to make a move and kill or deceive players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Step away from the table and turn your house into a real-life murder mystery party. Turn off the lights and Bring Your Own Flashlight (BYOF) if you dare to play in the dark.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
